OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FA number of councils across the North
OL,8,FWest have responded following a High
OL,9,FCourt judgement which ruled that
OL,10,Fasylum seekers could not be housed at
OL,11,Fa hotel in Epping following a legal
OL,12,Fchallenge.
OL,14,FBlackpool Council, Lancashire County
OL,15,FCouncil, Manchester City Council,
OL,16,FSouth Ribble Borough Council, Trafford
OL,17,FCouncil and Wirral Council have also
OL,18,Fsaid they will be reviewing the
OL,19,Fimplications of Tuesday's ruling.
