OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FIt comes as the Mayor for Greater
OL,8,FManchester, Andy Burnham, says the way
OL,9,Fhotels are used to house asylum
OL,10,Fseekers is 'not acceptable' and that
OL,11,F'real change' is necessary.
OL,13,F"The scandalous thing is the way in
OL,14,Fwhich the Home Office has dismissed
OL,15,Fthose concerns and ran roughshod over
OL,16,Flocal councils," he told BBC Radio
OL,17,FManchester. "Often you would get a day
OL,18,For two's notification. That's not good
OL,19,Fenough."
