OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FConservative-led Epping Forest
OL,8,FDistrict Council argued that it was
OL,9,Fseeking an injunction due to
OL,10,F"unprecedented levels of protest and
OL,11,Fdisruption" in connection with asylum
OL,12,Fseeker accommodation.
OL,14,FBarristers for the council said that
OL,15,Fthe site's "sole lawful use" was as a
OL,16,Fhotel and that Somani Hotels had
OL,17,Fbreached planning rules by using it to
OL,18,Fhouse asylum seekers.
