OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FIn his judgment, Mr Justice Eyre said
OL,8,Fthat while the council had not
OL,9,F"definitively established" that Somani
OL,10,FHotels had breached planning rules,
OL,11,F"the strength of the claimant's case
OL,12,Fis such that it weighs in favour" of
OL,13,Fgranting the injunction.
OL,15,FIt's thought councils across the
OL,16,Fcountry are now preparing their own
OL,17,Flegal challenges.
