OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FEarlier this month, rival groups
OL,8,Fprotested outside a hotel in Greater
OL,9,FManchester which is housing asylum
OL,10,Fseekers.
