OL,13,Foutside Cresta Court in Altrincham on
OL,14,F8 August.
OL,16,FThe opposing groups were separated by
OL,17,Fa dual carriageway with dozens of
OL,18,Fpolice assembled on the central
OL,19,Freservation of the A56 Church Street.
