OL,11,FBlackpool Council (Labour-controlled)
OL,13,FBlackpool Council has previously
OL,14,Fvoiced its opposition to the Metropole
OL,15,Fbeing used to house refugees.
OL,17,FHowever, the authority was keen to
OL,18,Fstress that the situation at the
OL,19,FMetropole was "different" from that at
OL,20,FEpping.
