OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FThe hotel in the resort is housing
OL,8,Ffamilies, rather than single males,
OL,9,Fand the council's objections have been
OL,10,Fover the building's unsuitability for
OL,11,Fhosting vulnerable people fleeing
OL,12,Fpersecution.
OL,14,FNevertheless, the Metropole, which
OL,15,Ffirst started to house asylum seekers
OL,16,Fin September 2021, has continued to
OL,17,Fattract a number of protesters in the
OL,18,Fpast year.
