OL,3,CHow have our councils responded
OL,4,Cfollowing the asylum hotel court
OL,5,Cruling?
OL,7,FA Blackpool Council spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Since the start of the use of The
OL,9,FMetropole for this purpose, we've been
OL,10,Fclear that it is not a suitable
OL,11,Flocation for asylum seekers fleeing
OL,12,Fabuse and persecution. We believe this
OL,13,Fuse should be brought to an end as
OL,14,Fsoon as possible.
OL,16,F"The Metropole in Blackpool is
OL,17,Fdifferent to the hotel in Epping in a
OL,18,Fnumber of ways. The hotel here is one
OL,19,Fof only a few that is home to
OL,20,Ffamilies, rather than single males who
OL,21,Fmight be sharing rooms.
